{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"11d2881414","title":"关于找草书字帖给田家英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0155efbafc","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"11d2881414"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"2491e11a39","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王菱之，东晋书法家。13]于右任千字文，指书法家于右任（曾长期担任国民党政府监察院院长）选用历代草书名家的草字双勾而成的《标准草书范本千字文》"},{"id":"7a35239dbc","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"草决歌，指明代韩道亨所书草楷对照的《草决百韵歌》。"},{"id":"dd7f16e982","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"郑振锋，当时任文化部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a2e21969fd","type":"title","text":"关于找草书字帖给田家英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"},{"id":"2491e11a39","type":"paragraph","text":"田家英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"},{"id":"7a35239dbc","type":"paragraph","text":"请将已存各种草书字帖清出给我，包括若干拓本（王菱之等），于右任千字文以及草决歌。此外，请向故宫博物院负责人（是否郑振锋？）一询，可否借阅那里的各种草书手迹若干，如可，应开单据，以便按件清还。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"},{"id":"dd7f16e982","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"},{"id":"7ae661c503","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"},{"id":"1947bedd84","type":"paragraph","text":"田家英，当时任毛泽东的秘书。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"11d2881414"}],"page":{"id":"27bfcfe5a0","public